---
Geraldine POLY : coach décoration, consultante Feng Shui
description: |
  Geraldine POLY : Coach décoration et consultante Feng Shui à Bordeaux. Je propose des services de coach décoration pour des espaces ou on se sent bien. J'accompagne les particuliers et les professionnels dans leurs projets de décoration et d'aménagement intérieur.
permalink: /
layout: default
---

<div class="pb-16">
  <section class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 md:gap-4">
    <h1 class="hidden sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl tracking-widest sm:block mt-8">GERALDINE POLY</h1>

    <%#= render Logo.new class: "w-40 sm:hidden fill-primary" %>

    <h2 class="tracking-widest text-gray text-xl text-center not-prose">
      <span class="inline-block">Coach décoration</span>
      <span class="hidden sm:inline-block"> ~ </span>
      <span class="inline-block">Consultante Feng Shui</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="hidden md:block w-full">
      <%= render CloudinaryImage.new(width: 866, height: 375, image_id: "tom/banner1", loading: "eager", class: "hidden md:block w-full", alt: "Géraldine POLY : une décoration qui fait du bien") %>
    </div>
    <div class="md:hidden">
      <%= render CloudinaryImage.new(width: 866, height: 600, image_id: "tom/banner1", loading: "eager", class: "md:hidden", alt: "Géraldine POLY : une décoration qui fait du bien") %>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-xl tracking-wider text-accent text-center text-gray hidden md:block">
      Une décoration qui fait du bien
    </h2>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-8">
    <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded p-8 flex flex-col gap-4">
      <h2>La newsletter déco qui fait du bien</h2>
      Tous les mois, je vous partage mes conseils déco et Feng Shui pour vous sentir bien chez vous.

      <a href="https://geraldinepoly.substack.com/subscribe" class="btn btn-primary self-start">Inscription</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <h2 class="mb-12 mt-20 text-primary text-center sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl tracking-widest">Réalisations</h2>
  <section class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-4 lg:flex-row lg:items-start lg:justify-between lg:gap-8" id="projects">
    <% collections.projects.resources.last(3).each do |project| %>
      <span class="flex flex-col">
        <h3><%= project.data.title %></h3>
        <a href="<%= project.relative_url %>">
          <%= render CloudinaryImage.new(width: 500, height: 300, image_id: project.data.image_id, loading: "lazy", shadow: true, alt: "Image du projet : #{project.data.title}") %>
        </a>
      </span>
    <% end %>
  </section>

  <h2 class="mb-12 mt-20 text-primary text-center sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl tracking-widest">Témoignages</h2>
  <section>
    <div class="glider-contain" data-controller="carousel">
      <div data-carousel-target="slides" class="glider">
        <% collections.testimonials.resources.each do |testimonials| %>
          <div class="w-full md:px-32">
          <blockquote class="italic font-semibold">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-400 mb-4" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 18 14">
              <path d="M6 0H2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4v1a3 3 0 0 1-3 3H2a1 1 0 0 0 0 2h1a5.006 5.006 0 0 0 5-5V2a2 2 0 0 0-2-2Zm10 0h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4v1a3 3 0 0 1-3 3h-1a1 1 0 0 0 0 2h1a5.006 5.006 0 0 0 5-5V2a2 2 0 0 0-2-2Z"/>
            </svg>
            <div><%= testimonials.data.text %></div>
          </blockquote>
          <div class="text-right">~ <%= testimonials.data.name %></div>
        </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>

      <button aria-label="Previous" data-carousel-target="previous" class="glider-prev hidden md:block">«</button>
      <button aria-label="Next" data-carousel-target="next" class="glider-next hidden md:block">»</button>
      <div data-carousel-target="dots" role="tablist" class="glider-dots"></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
